{% extends "layout.html" %}

{% block title %}About — Stella Fusaro{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<div class="video-background">
  <video autoplay muted loop playsinline>
    <source src="{{ url_for('static', filename='homepage.mp4') }}" type="video/mp4">
    Your browser does not support the video tag.
  </video>
</div>

<section class="about-overlay">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-image">
      <img src="{{ url_for('static', filename='stella.png') }}" alt="Stella Fusaro">
    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <h1>Stella Fusaro</h1>
      <p>
        Hi, I’m Stella — a filmmaker, designer, and computer science graduate based in New York. My work lives at the intersection of visual storytelling and technical precision. Whether I’m editing a short film, designing for impact, or building websites from scratch, I believe in creating work that is intentional, bold, and thoughtful.
      </p>

      <p>
        I graduated from Columbia University with a degree in Computer Science, Math, and Film. My experience spans directing and editing short films, crafting creative video media for advertisements, and coding dynamic, responsive websites (like this one!).
      </p>

      <p>
        I also program for WKCR-FM, where you can hear me on Wednesdays from 3–6pm hosting a show dedicated to film scores — with a focus on marginalized composers, including women and people of color. When I can, I also love curating classical music programming.
      </p>

      <p>
        Outside of this work, I spend a lot of time in the ballet world — both dancing and watching. I’m a member of the Junior Council at the American Ballet Theatre, and I love choreographing pieces whenever I can. I also enjoy planning events, and I’m a certified bartender from the Columbia School of Mixology. Crafting cocktails is one of my favorite creative outlets.
      </p>

      <p>
        Want to collaborate? <a href="mailto:stellacfusaro@gmail.com">Let’s talk.</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .video-background {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100vw;
    height: 100vh;
    z-index: -1;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .video-background video {
    width: 100vw;
    height: 100vh;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
  }

  .about-overlay {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    font-family: sans-serif;
    color: black;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-image {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-image img {
      height: 100%;
      max-height: 600px;
      width: auto;
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .about-text {
      flex: 2;
      max-width: 650px;
    }
  }

  .about-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .about-text h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .about-text a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    color: #333;
  }

  .about-text a:hover {
    color: black;
  }
</style>

{% endblock %}

